    "Section 5 describes the set of experiments carried out and discusses the results.",
    "Section 6 details the threats to the validity of the study and, finally, the conclusions are discussed in Section 7.",
    "Related workGreat interest has been pointed in the last years to DSSs given their utility to assist humans in making high-quality decisions based on domain-specific information [10].",
